title: Satellite suicide
info:
Placed second in Outline 2004 MP3 compo

[ satellite suicide ]

I'm circling the earth
everything is so quiet
I'm at maximum height
I'm a satellite

They left me here above
when the human race died
now I'm here all alone
all day and night

I am so lonely

From now and then
alien visitors came
they scanned this place
then flew away

Up here in space

my final wish
I want to kill myself.
